</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_581_r1l24"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt . C . volland als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe eẅch <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l25">ſey daʒ Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnwıllen haben ſüllt von ʒugrıff <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe Jr dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l26">Stıft von <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> getan habt etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ſehen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l27">wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teıls nıht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . ʒugrıff vnd <expan>beſchedıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> der lande . Wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l28"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wölt Jr <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem weıſʒen <expan>ſunnt<ex>ag</ex></expan> <expan>ſchıerıſtkünft<ex>ig</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l29">ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo ſüllt Jr <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt ʒu vnd von vns für vns vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l30">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> ııȷ tag geleyt haben / alſdenn <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_581_r1l31">rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_581" id="289v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Conczen Volland </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst. <expan>C<ex>oncz</ex></expan> Volland,
                        als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch
                                <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz ir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> unwillen haben süllt von zugriff
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir dem stift von
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> getan habt, etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu sehen wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils niht
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zugriff und
                            <expan>beschedigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> der lande. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wölt ir
                        <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <app><note><q type="date">weiszen
                            <expan>sunnt<ex>ag</ex></expan>
<expan>schieristkünft<ex>ig</ex></expan></q>11.04.1423</note></app>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so
                        süllt ir <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
                        iii tag geleyt haben; alsdenn <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr rede
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
